subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: David Ferrer advanced to the Australian Open quarterfinal after a hard-fought challenge by Kei Nishikori of Japan, and No. 19 seed Ekaterina Makarova ousted fifth-seeded Angelique Kerber.
